org.ssa4j
Annotation Type ScrapeDataRecordField

@Documented
@Target(value={METHOD,FIELD})
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface ScrapeDataRecordField

Method level annotation used to describe how a particular field of a DataRecord maps to the class method. This should only be use with property structure "set" methods.

Author:
Rodney Aiglstorfer

Required Element Summary
 java.lang.String name
          The name of the field as communicated by Screen-Scraper
 
Optional Element Summary
 java.lang.String format
          A format string used to assist in the convertion of raw field values into the expected class types.
